    public class SyntaxTreeRuleIndividual
extends net.sf.jclec.syntaxtree.SyntaxTreeIndividual
implements IClassifierIndividual
    SyntaxTreeRuleIndividual for SyntaxTree rules.

    Implements an individual whose genotype is a SyntaxTree (extends SyntaxTreeIndividual) and the phenotype is a rule.

    Author:
    Amelia Zafra, Sebastian Ventura, Jose M. Luna, Alberto Cano, Juan Luis Olmo
